properties.Title: Storm Surge Warning In Effect
properties.Summary:
Description: Higher than normal water levels with large waves are expected near the coast. Warning of potential breaking sea conditions and overwash issued jointly by Fisheries and Oceans Canada (Science) and the Meteorological Service of Canada - Quebec Region on 2021-02-02. Higher than normal water levels and large waves are expected near the coast on February 3rd, 2021. An intense low pressure system will move up the American Eastern Seaboard and give strong to high northeasterly winds over the areas specified below.
